    <bpmn:sendTask id="informSelectedTable" name="Inform Selected Table" zeebe:modelerTemplate="Template_2terfy1" zeebe:modelerTemplateVersion="1" zeebe:modelerTemplateIcon="data:image/svg+xml;base64,">
      <bpmn:extensionElements>
        <zeebe:taskDefinition type="io.camunda:sendMessage:1" retries="3" />
        <zeebe:ioMapping>
